{"TopicId":213035,"ForumId":196,"TopicTitle":"Pause \u0026 unpaused pop ups in menu","CreatedByName":"PsykoMonkee87","CreatedById":226482,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-26T06:48:40Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"PsykoMonkee87","CreatedById":226482,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-26T06:48:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003EKSP Version -\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E 0.1.0.0.20892\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003EOperating System and version\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E -\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E Windows 11 (playing/streamed via Parsec to a Macbook)\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003ECPU and GPU models -\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E Ryzen 3600 - Nvidia RTX3070\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDescription of the bug:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nWhen pressing the \u0027,\u0027 and \u0027.\u0027 keys when on the main after quitting to main menu, the \u0027Game Paused\u0027 and \u0027Game Unpaused\u0027 pop-ups appear and the menu background animations pause and unpause\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESteps to Replicate\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nLoad\u00A0 into the game\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nToggle the time-warp keys (comma \u0026amp; period) on the main menu and see no effect\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003ELoad or start a game/campaign\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nSelect \u0027Quit to main menu\u0027 from the in-game menu\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nToggle the time-warp keys (comma \u0026amp; period) on the main menu to see the \u0027Game paused\u0027 and \u0027Game unpaused\u0027 pop-ups and the background animation pause and unpause\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-02-26T06:49:44Z\u0022 title=\u002202/26/2023 06:49  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 26, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by PsykoMonkee87\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EAdded KSP2 version\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}